#

Caramel Apple Pie

65 min
$12
320 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 8

Allergens:

GlutenDairy

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Dessert

Tags:

DessertPieFallSweet

Description

A warm, gooey apple pie with a rich caramel twist, perfect for dessert lovers!

Ingredients

  • pie crust (store-bought): 1
  • apples (peeled, cored, and sliced): 6 cups
  • granulated sugar: 3/4 cup
  • brown sugar: 1/4 cup
  • cinnamon: 1 tsp
  • nutmeg: 1/4 tsp
  • lemon juice: 2 tbsp
  • caramel sauce: 1 cup
  • butter (for dotting): 2 tbsp
